Xu3A9/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">champagnepapi (@champagnepapi) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>他与 J.Cole 巡演的下一场演出定于 3 月 6 日星期三在新奥尔良的 Smoothie King Center 举行。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fdrake-tickets%2Fartist%2F1319371" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处获取最后一刻的门票。</a></p><p>在其他地方，德雷克最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-pays-tribute-to-two-fans-killed-outside-his-st-louis-concert-3595607">向上个月在圣路易斯的演出外遇害的一对母女表示敬意</a>。</p><p>他在周三（2 月 28 日）的一场演出中谈到了这些问题，鼓励他的粉丝相互联系。</p><p>在其他新闻中，德雷克在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-reveals-she-was-shot-tory-lanez-2708559">2020 年</a>因射杀<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion)</a>双脚<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-sentenced-to-10-years-in-prison-for-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-3480329">而被判处 10 年监禁</a>后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/drake-calls-for-tory-lanez-to-be-freed-after-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-case-3593213">公开呼吁释放</a>托里·拉内兹<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tory-lanez">(Tory Lanez)，</a>引发了争议。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-found-guilty-of-shooting-megan-thee-stallion-3371194">拉内兹于 2022 年 12 月被判犯有</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-reveals-she-was-shot-tory-lanez-2708559">枪击事件</a>相关的三项重罪，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanez-says-hes-in-great-spirits-during-first-month-in-prison-3504600">于次年 8 月开始服刑 10 年</a>。不过，据报道，由于他已经在监狱和软禁中度过了一段时间<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tory-lanezs-megan-thee-stallion-shooting-sentence-will-likely-be-reduced-to-nine-years-3481223">，他的刑期可能会减至九年</a>。</p><p> <a